race.comment: A staying race with a few key chances but a long tail. ALPINE ROCKET (3) was plain last start but his best is definitely good enough to win this. He will get a likable set-up from barrier three with Todd Pannell aboard. The senior jockey may make the difference in a race with plenty of apprentices engaged. SMILING ASSASSIN (1) is a prolific winner that was placed in a stronger race. He may be getting on in years but you can't discount him in these SA staying races. Stablemate AMBITIOUS CREEK (6) can run in the minor money if things go his way. JUGAN (5) and TYITA (7) are also worth including for value.
